--[[ 
Colors are defined as {red, green, blue, alpha}
(Values are between 0 and 1)

Default colors are:
backgroundColor = {0.15, 0.15, 0.15, 1}
foregroundColor = {0.75, 0.29, 0, 0.8}
textColor       = {1, 1, 1, 0.7}  
buttonColor     = {1, 0, 0, 1} 
hotbuttonColor  = {0, 1, 0, 1}
shadows         = true

